The daemon can be started with the following command line.  It accesses its dependencies from the
lib folder and it requires that all required plugins are compiled and deployed to 
$CATALINA_HOME/waspPlugins.

java -Xms128m -Xmx512m -XX:PermSize=128m -XX:MaxPermSize=256m -Dcatalina.home=$CATALINA_HOME -cp "target/wasp-daemon-0.1.0-SNAPSHOT-release/wasp-daemon-0.1.0-SNAPSHOT/wasp-daemon-0.1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar:$CATALINA_HOME/waspPlugins/*" edu.yu.einstein.wasp.daemon.StartDaemon

